#: ../../source/ambd_arduino/examples/peripheral/Flash Memory - Use Flash Memory Larger Than 4K.rst:20
msgid "Flash Memory API uses memory of 4K bytes, which is normally sufficient for most application. However, larger memory can be provided by specifying a specific memory address and required size."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/ambd_arduino/examples/peripheral/Flash Memory - Use Flash Memory Larger Than 4K.rst:23
